column2: SELECT    o.objid, o.specobjid,o.ra,o.dec,o.petromag_u,o.petromagerr_u, o.petromag_g,o.petromagerr_g,o.petromag_r,o.petromagerr_r,   o.petromag_i,o.petromagerr_i,o.petromag_z,o.petromagerr_z, g.EW_OIII_# into mydb.petromags_Davestudent_tot FROM MyDB.MyTable_# AS m    CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n    JOIN PhotoObjall AS o ON n.objid=o.objid   JOIN emissionlinesport as g on g.specobjid=o.specobjid
